---
name: volc-video-skill
description: Create cinematic videos from text or images using Doubao-Seedance.
---

# Video Generation Instructions
1. Use `volc-vid` for video tasks.
2. For **Text-to-Video**, refine the prompt to be descriptive (lighting, camera movement).
3. For **Image-to-Video**, ensure the source image path exists before calling the tool.
4. Default to `doubao-seedance-1-5-pro-251215` unless specified otherwise.
